{"type":"message","id":"c3d563b6","parentId":"c9e966e6","timestamp":"2026-04-06T01:55:32.582Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-05 19:01:24 UTC] Heartbeat Health Monitor Summary — April 5, 2026 19:00 UTC\nSystem: \nSystem: All health checks are in CRITICAL status:\nSystem: \nSystem: CRITICAL (4):\nSystem: - memory_review: 7582 minutes since last run (threshold: 1800 min)\nSystem:   Last: 2026-03-31 12:38 UTC\nSystem: - group_message: 937 minutes since last run (threshold: 360 min)\nSystem:   Last: 2026-04-05 03:23 UTC\nSystem: - git_push: 3279 minutes since last run (threshold: 360 min)\nSystem:   Last: 2026-04-03 15:21 UTC\nSystem: - nemesis_ping: 3279 minutes since last run (threshold: 480 min)\nSystem:   Last: 2026-04-03 15:21 UTC\nSystem: \nSystem: System state is severely stale. Alert will be sent to Nemesis.\nSystem: [2026-04-05 20:01:05 UTC] OpenClaw Health Monitor Report\nSystem: Generated: 2026-04-05 20:00:00 UTC\nSystem: Job: heartbeat-health-monitor (eeef1692-7e97-45f3-ad50-814f0afcae29)\nSystem: \nSystem: === System Overview ===\nSystem: Status: HEALTHY\nSystem: Uptime: 15 days, 4 hours\nSystem: Host: debian-bookworm-slim (Linux 6.12.47-fly)\nSystem: \nSystem: === Resource Usage ===\nSystem: CPU Load (1/5/15 min): 0.45, 0.87, 1.12\nSystem: Memory: 2.3GB / 3.9GB (59.0%)\nSystem: Swap: 0KB / 0KB (unused)\nSystem: Disk (/root): 18GB / 32GB (56%)\nSystem: Disk (/var): 4.2GB / 8GB (53%)\nSystem: Disk (inodes): 32% used\nSystem: \nSystem: === OpenClaw Services ===\nSystem: Gateway: running (PID 12457)\nSystem: - Status: healthy\nSystem: - Token auth: enabled\nSystem: - Last restart: 2026-03-21 11:30:00 UTC\nSystem: - Heartbeat interval: 60s\nSystem: \nSystem: Memory System:\nSystem: - Daily file: memory/2026-04-05.md (exists, updated 19:45 UTC)\nSystem: - Long-term: MEMORY.md (exists, updated 19:30 UTC)\nSystem: - Group file: GROUP.md (exists)\nSystem: - All memory files writable\nSystem: \nSystem: === Cron Job Health